    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[Git 代理设置]]></title>
      <url>https://ymfeelcn.github.io/2017/01/07/Git-%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Git默认clone或push速度很慢，原因你懂的，下面以shadowsocks做代理例子，输入以下命令即可<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git config --global http.proxy <span class="string">'socks5://127.0.0.1:1080'</span></div><div class="line">$ git config --global https.proxy <span class="string">'socks5://127.0.0.1:1080'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 这样就OK了，可以输入以下命令查看是否设置成功</span></div><div class="line">$ git config --list</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如果想取消代理设置，输入以下命令即可<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git config --global --unset http.proxy</div><div class="line">$ git config --global --unset https.proxy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这样就可以愉快的用Git啦。</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[Git SSH Key 生成步骤]]></title>
      <url>https://ymfeelcn.github.io/2017/01/06/Git-SSH-Key-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Git是分布式的代码管理工具，远程的代码管理是基于SSH的，所以要使用远程的Git则需要SSH的配置。<br>github的SSH配置如下：</p>
<h2 id="一、设置Git的user-name和email："><a href="#一、设置Git的user-name和email：" class="headerlink" title="一、设置Git的user name和email："></a>一、设置Git的user name和email：</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入你自己的用户名和邮箱</span></div><div class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"ymfeelcn"</span></div><div class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"ymfeelcn@gmail.com"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="二、生成SSH密钥过程："><a href="#二、生成SSH密钥过程：" class="headerlink" title="二、生成SSH密钥过程："></a>二、生成SSH密钥过程：</h2><p>1.查看是否已经有了ssh密钥：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果没有密钥则不会有此文件夹,为以下提示</span></div><div class="line">bash: <span class="built_in">cd</span>: /c/Users/Administrator/.ssh: No such file or directory</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注意：如果你已经生成了密钥，想重新生成，则直接删除 .ssh 这个目录即可，最好先自己备份哦。</p>
<p>2.开始生成密钥：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 这里填写自己的邮箱</span></div><div class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"ymfeelcn@gmail.com"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 会出现以下提示</span></div><div class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</div><div class="line">Enter file <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">which</span> to save the key (/c/Users/Administrator/.ssh/id_rsa):  <span class="comment"># 按回车</span></div><div class="line">Created directory <span class="string">'/c/Users/Administrator/.ssh'</span>.</div><div class="line">Enter passphrase (empty <span class="keyword">for</span> no passphrase):		<span class="comment"># 如果想设置密码则写密码，若想空则回车</span></div><div class="line">Enter same passphrase again: 					<span class="comment"># 如果想设置密码则写密码，若想空则回车</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 出现以下则说明正常生成啦</span></div><div class="line">Your identification has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Administrator/.ssh/id_rsa.</div><div class="line">Your public key has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Administrator/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.</div><div class="line">The key fingerprint is:</div><div class="line">SHA256:TYuNEGgM+UBHPE2pcI0MDs/GRr2iHwr473/fDJBev7s ymfeelcn@gmail.com</div><div class="line">The key<span class="string">'s randomart image is:</span></div><div class="line">+---[RSA 2048]----+</div><div class="line">|..=Xo*o.         |</div><div class="line">| B+.@ +.         |</div><div class="line">|  B* +.   .      |</div><div class="line">| o. +  . B .     |</div><div class="line">|.. .    S =      |</div><div class="line">|+ .    . o .     |</div><div class="line">|.+ .    . . .    |</div><div class="line">|. o     .  + .   |</div><div class="line">|   oo... .. Eo   |</div><div class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</div><div class="line">Administrator@PC-Ming MINGW64 ~ (master)</div><div class="line">$ cd ~/.ssh</div><div class="line">$ ls</div><div class="line">id_rsa  id_rsa.pub</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>3.最后得到了两个文件：id_rsa和id_rsa.pub</p>
<h1 id="三、登录GitHub设置SSH"><a href="#三、登录GitHub设置SSH" class="headerlink" title="三、登录GitHub设置SSH"></a>三、登录GitHub设置SSH</h1><p>1.打开 <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub</a> , 用自己的账号登录，然后打开用户设置，SSH and GPG Keys，添加密钥，步骤如下：Setting-&gt;SSH and GPG Keys-&gt;New SSH Key<br>2.表单里 Title 名称随便写，自己能分辨就行，Key 则用记事本打开刚刚生成的 id_rsa.pub 文件，把里面的内容复制进入，然后点 Add SSH Key 按钮，即可<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Administrator@PC-Ming MINGW64 ~ (master)</div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</div><div class="line">Administrator@PC-Ming MINGW64 ~ (master)</div><div class="line">$ ls</div><div class="line">id_rsa  id_rsa.pub</div><div class="line">Administrator@PC-Ming MINGW64 ~ (master)</div><div class="line">$ cat id_rsa.pub</div><div class="line">ssh-rsa AAAAB3NzaC1yc2EAAAADAQABAAABAQDEwf... <span class="comment"># 这里就省略啦。</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="四、测试SSH配置是否成功"><a href="#四、测试SSH配置是否成功" class="headerlink" title="四、测试SSH配置是否成功"></a>四、测试SSH配置是否成功</h1><p>按下面操作即可，如果出现了你的用户名，则表示成功啦。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入以下命令，等待一会</span></div><div class="line">$ ssh git@github.com</div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 若出现以下提示，不要着急，输入 yes即可</span></div><div class="line">The authenticity of host <span class="string">'github.com (192.30.253.113)'</span> can<span class="string">'t be established.</span></div><div class="line">RSA key fingerprint is SHA256:nThbg6kXUpJWGl7E1IGOCspRomTxdCARLviKw6E5SY8.</div><div class="line">Are you sure you want to continue connecting (yes/no)?    # yes</div><div class="line"># 出现你的用户名，则表示成功啦</div><div class="line">Hi ymfeelcn! You've successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</div><div class="line">Connection to github.com closed.</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="GitHub配置SSH-Keys就全部OK啦。"><a href="#GitHub配置SSH-Keys就全部OK啦。" class="headerlink" title="GitHub配置SSH Keys就全部OK啦。"></a>GitHub配置SSH Keys就全部OK啦。</h1>]]></content>
    </entry>
    
